<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从那以后，艾伦的身边就一直有人陪着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每个抱她的人都会抱得紧紧的，这样她就不会飘走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>床上和婴儿车上都有丝带，不管去哪里，她都会被绑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她可怜的父母天天都在担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，国王在数他的金币。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的金币有重量，”他悲伤地想，“但我的女儿一点儿重量也没有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49839</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，国王听到有人在哭。是王后！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王急忙向她跑去：“我的王后，怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62681</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的艾伦怎么办？”王后哭着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她太轻了，如果我们再失去她怎么办？”王后擤了擤鼻涕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76776</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这确实是个大问题！”国王担忧地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“想想艾伦结婚生子后会发生什么？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们的王国将到处都是飘着的婴儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一个主意。”王后慢慢地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王笑了：“我的王后，你总是有好主意！是什么主意？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以去拜访一下你的姐姐。”王后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王紧张地咳嗽起来：“去……拜访艾格尼丝？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113964</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，向她道歉，说我们不是故意忘记邀请她的。”王后说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后你必须请求她解除咒语。求求你了，亲爱的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王叹了口气，拍了拍王后的肩膀：“别哭了，我明天就去。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，国王去拜访艾格尼丝。仆人端来了茶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我……嗯……”国王揉搓着手里的餐巾纸，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最近一切都好吧？我来找你，是想谈一件非常重要的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝眯起眼睛：“是吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是说咒语。”国王说，“我知道洗礼那天，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为没有收到请柬，你很生气，所以你就对艾伦施了咒语，现在她……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咒语？”艾格尼丝大声笑了起来，“多么可笑！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你还是像以前一样，太没有耐心了，弟弟！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205856</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等你的傻女儿长大，她自然就不会那么轻了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，你只需要耐心地……改正你的品行！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“改正我的品行？”国王说，“你这是什么意思？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“意思就是，你要努力成为一个更好的人。”艾格尼丝冷笑着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来教你！就从多尊重你的姐姐开始！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>